2006-08-18 21:26  lennart

	* src/pulsecore/log.c, src/pulsecore/log.h: rework logging
	  subsystem, to implicitly include __FILE__ in pa_log() calls. In
	  addition we now record the line numbers and function names of
	  pa_log calls. However, those are only shown If $PULSE_LOG_META is
	  set.

