	* src/polyp/stream.c, src/polypcore/modinfo.c,
	  src/polypcore/module.c, src/polypcore/pipe.h,
	  src/polypcore/protocol-esound.c, src/polypcore/random.c,
	  src/polypcore/x11wrap.c, src/utils/padsp.c: Fix warnings.

2006-05-24 13:22  ossman

	* configure.ac: Remove the exceedingly anal warnings. It's
	  impossible to write a non-trivial
	  C program and not trigger these.

2006-05-24 08:14  ossman

	* src/utils/padsp.c: Fix stray \

2006-05-24 02:13  lennart

	* src/utils/padsp.c: implement a /dev/mixer interface

2006-05-24 00:42  lennart

	* src/utils/padsp.c: fix playback of small sound files

2006-05-23 23:57  lennart

	* src/utils/padsp.c: implement emulation of /dev/sndstat

2006-05-23 23:06  lennart

	* src/utils/padsp.c: - use pthread_atfork() to disable open sound
	  streams in the child after a fork.
	  Obviusly sound won't work in child process but at least we don't
	  leak fds
	  from the parent. Now any operation on the device fd in the child
	  will result
	  in an EBADF error, which seems somewhat clean to me.
	  
	  - flush our unix socket properly on RESET ioctl

2006-05-23 16:37  lennart

	* src/utils/padsp.c: pass the binary name as client name to
	  polypaudio

2006-05-23 15:24  ossman

	* src/utils/padsp.c: Cast size_t to long to be more compatible with
	  64-bit systems.

2006-05-23 14:42  lennart

	* src, src/Makefile.am, src/utils/padsp.c, src/utils/padsp.in: add
	  new padsp utility: a $LD_PRELOAD wrapper for using the OSS API
	  with polypaudio

